Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要下的話  倒是希望能在早上就開始下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  只是覺得雨下得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你沒帶傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是我疏忽大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要我借你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,借給我  你用什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你是二刀流?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我只帶了一把傘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我還要幫老師做事  所以暫時還不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在我完事之後  這時雨應該就會停了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說這雨會越下越大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道明天操場還能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事  你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我似乎是偏火屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可能會被人懷疑雨是我的弱點屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別看我這樣  其實我水屬性也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我從來都沒有擔心過這個方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz331.6\pos(836,405)}這樣子啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz329.7\pos(513,501)}師傅、一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾說和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我買了河童雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這顏色真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得抓緊了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,河童?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是你值日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧  內卷要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷你有帶傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你帶伊萬莉一起撐回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒有帶傘  非常頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她現在應該還在樓梯口那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒也是  這麼大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,武田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,收上來的筆記本我就放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我還要收拾一下東西  就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  那能麻煩你幫忙補充一下粉筆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就在器材室右邊那個架子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看來還要花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是香織嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我今天差點遲到  所以忘記帶傘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,人家很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  瑞瑞你的傘我就借走了哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便給我拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我這絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,香織!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺禍不單行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,香織那傢伙  居然真帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後我馬上來到這裡找她  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是淚水呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亞爾希安戰記第二章  是和馬莉安娜訣別的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,才不對  你這樣會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  你可別小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是有水之精靈的加護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,師傅  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  原來你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真像那兩個人會搞出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然後為什麼你會留下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友把你的傘借走了不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\b0\bord1\shad0\c&H453A38&\move(308,207,348,227)\3c&HFFFFFF&}香織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要和我一起用這把傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,香織  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,打…打擾了…
